projectInfo.instructions:
Imagery
=======
Please use the **Bing Imagery** to do your mapping. 

Please map all buildings
======================
There are not many buildings in the area, but generally the buildings squared. Please **map all** of them.  

* In iD: draw an area and label it as “Building”, then correct for right angles with the “S” key

* In JOSM: draw an area and use the tag “building=yes”; then correct for right angles using the “Q” key - OR use the building plugin
